data.description: You'll love this beautiful unit in the desirable Riverbend Community! This large model has a multi-level open floor plan with an abundance of windows, high vaulted ceilings and a modern feel! There is a downstairs living room and loft with lots of natural light, chandelier, whitewashed reclaimed wood accent wall and full bath. Formal dining room with candelabra style chandelier, custom shelves and reclaimed wood accent wall. Spacious kitchen with custom brick accents, granite counters, recessed lighting, stainless steel appliances, cabinets galore and breakfast bar. The adjoining family room has lots of windows, gas fireplace and reclaimed wood accent wall. Half bath with pedestal sink, custom light and mirror and half paneled wall. Additional features include custom paint, window shutters, ceiling fans, stained concrete and wood laminate flooring. All bedrooms are upstairs along with hall bath and laundry room. Primary suite has separate tub and shower, dual sinks, walk-in closet and bonus side closet. The bedrooms and upstairs baths have been freshly painted. Backyard has artificial grass and room for BBQ and seating area. Attached 2-car garage with extra storage. Interior location close to the pool/spa and within walking distance to Steve Ambriz Memorial Park! HOA amenities include community pool/spa and WIFI! Make this one your new home!
